node.text: Omg ❤️ creamy rich burnt cheesecake sounds so good 😊

🧀Creamy and Rich burnt cheesecake from @oliviarestaurant_sg is hard to resist! The blue cheese in the cake isn’t too overpowering which makes it acceptable to a person who doesn’t really like the smell! ⁣
⁣
Overall still one of the more delicious cheesecake out there! ❤️❤️ Which Place sells your favourite basque burnt cheesecake? Let me know in the comments section below 😋😋⁣
